When my parents brought that black record back from brazil in 1973 it was just a shock, for them, then for us: how were such splendid voice tones possible ? how was it possible to bring so much melancholy or fantasy into music? Even if you don&amp;#039;t understand Portuguese or Brazilian dialect you have the feeling you just understand it crytal clear: this recording can help you to go through different moods, love, sadness, etc. Perhaps the best Bossa Nova record ever.
